Package: hRUV
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchical approach to normalise large-scale metabolomics data
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Taiyun", "Kim", email = "taiyun.kim91@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: hRUV is a package developed for removal of unwanted variation in 
    Mass-spectrometry based metabolomics data. hRUV consists of various approaches 
    to removing intra- and inter-batch effects and a systematic evaluation framework.
